{"tid":342925,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡若蓮稱「工作關係」辭任教聯會 已獲接納","createTime":"2017-08-01T04:31:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T04:44:27.000Z","uid":42804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0afa3aa5c3f9e0b0f96d5e4ea2e97ccdf8e58713","tid":342925,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:31:30.000Z","msg":"今屆政府今日將公佈首批副局長及政治助理名單，當中最受爭議的是盛傳會擔任教育局副局長的教聯會副會長蔡若蓮，甚至引起教育界聯署反對。有指蔡若蓮將在首批名單之上，今早教聯會主席黃錦良在電台節目證實，昨日收到蔡辭任教聯會副主席職務信件，而他亦已經接納。他指不評論蔡會否加入政府，惟應尊重政府任命。<br />\n<br />\n蔡若蓮為教聯會副主席及福建中學(小西灣)校長，有指將會出任教育局副局長，最快星期三可履新。黃錦良在節目中表示，蔡在辭職信中解釋因「工作關係」辭任。今早福建中學未見蔡的蹤影，學校職員指，蔡今早未有上班，亦不確定蔡今日會否回校。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57026977&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170801\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57026977%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170801&d=mVlYyMYxp8RAGMAxak8MbDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=fef6dc36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57026977%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170801&h=8f94159c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57026977&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170801</a>"},{"pid":"a4d28d592772f308d711cf5b6804b3cd0704ebe7","tid":342925,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0685d9efbbd7cc7bb8a94d4dd308d198f3d55d1a","tid":342925,"uid":52062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:44:27.000Z","msg":"關咩事 係佢成個人有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}